a private prison system

05:35.583 --> 05:37.316
run by extraction specialists.

05:37.317 --> 05:38.985
And if anybody is gonna know

05:38.986 --> 05:41.788
where Volkoff's prisoners are
held, it's these guys.

05:49.429 --> 05:54.532
Sarah, those guys used to work
for someone we know.

05:54.599 --> 05:56.900
After I secured the gold using
my handprint,

05:56.968 --> 05:59.803
