would be my funeral.

06:41.205 --> 06:43.307
That's it!

06:43.374 --> 06:46.243
Casey, I know how
to find your old team.

06:47.879 --> 06:49.746
We have to kill you.

06:49.747 --> 06:55.747
Transcrypt by www.addic7ed.com

07:34.215 --> 07:37.682
