for Colonel Casey?

07:39.918 --> 07:42.287
Well, yes, uh, General,
I believe we have

07:42.355 --> 07:44.356
a unique opportunity here
to set a trap

07:44.423 --> 07:46.824
for Casey's old team, who
happen to be Volkoff agents.

07:46.892 --> 07:48.693
If they think I'm dead,
they'll come for this.

07:48.694 --> 07:49.927
My handprint's the only way

07:49.928 --> 07:51.162
they're gonna access
that Iranian vault.

07:51.163 --> 07:52.363
Here's the plan:

07:52.364 --> 07:54.131
First, we spread the news
of Casey's death

07:54.132 --> 07:55.565
through all the back channels

07:55.566 --> 07:57.701
that civilians don't monitor
but Volkoff does.

07:57.768 --> 07:59.668
Next up, we kill the Colonel.

07:59.703 --> 08:00.969
You want him to play dead?

08:00.970 --> 08:01.970
