08:01.971 --> 08:03.239
When Casey's former team

08:03.240 --> 08:04.373
sees Casey's actual body,

08:04.374 --> 08:05.941
we believe they'll drop
their guard,

08:05.942 --> 08:07.043
giving us the upper hand.

08:07.044 --> 08:08.710
And then we'll move in.

08:08.711 --> 08:11.079
We will control every
entrance and exit.

08:11.146 --> 08:13.046
Snipers will posted
and at the ready.

08:13.048 --> 08:15.681
And the audience will
be filled with agents

08:15.749 --> 08:17.083
that we've planted there.

08:17.084 --> 08:20.519
All right. You've clearly
thought this through.

08:20.587 --> 08:21.720
The mission is a go.

08:21.721 --> 08:23.088
Thank you, General.

08:23.089 --> 08:25.589
Colonel Casey, Agent Walker,
you're both dismissed.

08:25.657 --> 08:29.192
I'd like a word
with Agent Bartowski alone.

08:36.599 --> 08:40.232
I'm impressed; you've really
progressed as a spy.

08:40.301 --> 08:43.366
Thank you, ma'am.
Thank you very much.

08:43.433 --> 08:45.902
