gonna use to kill me, hmm?

09:22.968 --> 09:24.001
What's it called,
Fake-a-deathanol?

09:24.002 --> 09:25.402
Cute.

09:25.403 --> 09:27.504
No. As a matter
of fact,

09:27.572 --> 09:29.506
it's called Tetrodotoxin.

09:29.574 --> 09:31.675
Normally it would just kill you
outright,

09:31.743 --> 09:33.076
but we've modified it so it'll

09:33.077 --> 09:34.344
just slow down your breathing
and heart rate.

09:34.345 --> 09:36.246
Outstanding.

09:36.314 --> 09:38.214
You will come across as being
very, very dead,

09:38.249 --> 09:40.383
but in actuality, you'll
be very much alive and awake-

09:40.451 --> 09:42.085
however, paralyzed.
I'll show you how it works.

09:42.086 --> 09:45.521
No, it's not like it's the first
time I ever faked my own death.

09:45.588 --> 09:48.089
