09:55.362 --> 09:57.530
how long the drug's effects will
last in your system,

09:57.597 --> 09:59.064
so I'm gonna take the liberty

09:59.065 --> 10:00.966
of stashing an extra hypo
on your person.

10:01.034 --> 10:03.601
I'd like a little alone time
before I die.

10:03.669 --> 10:05.637
One more thing,

10:05.704 --> 10:07.272
one more thing,
A little thing, uh...

10:07.273 --> 10:09.708
Because Sarah and I are gonna be
busy during all of this,

10:09.776 --> 10:12.644
